The main.css file:

p.one {
    padding: 5px;
    border: 2px solid #c0c0c0;
}
p.two {
    padding-top: 5px;
    border: 2px solid #c0c0c0;
}
p.three {
    padding-bottom: 5px;
    border: 2px solid #c0c0c0;
}
p.four {
    padding-left: 5px;
    border: 2px solid #c0c0c0;
}
p.five {
    padding-right: 5px;
    border: 2px solid #c0c0c0;
}

The main web page with the main.css linked :

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>CSS Lists Application</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="main.css">
    </head
    <body>
        <h3>CSS Padding Application</h3>
        <p class="one">Exercise of using padding property</p>
        <p class="two">Exercise of using padding-top property</p>
        <p class="three">Exercise of using padding-bottom property</p>
        <p class="four">Exercise of using padding-left property</p>
        <p class="five">Exercise of using padding-right property</p>
    </body>
</html>
